Heat the oil in a wok or large frying pan, add the chilli, garlic and ginger and stir fry for one minute.Add the pak choi and stir fry for 1-2 minutes, or until beginning to wilt.Add the soy sauce, sesame oil and lime juice and simmer for 1-2 minutes.Add the cooked noodles and stir well.To serve, place the salad into a serving bowl and garnish with lime wedges.